      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like everything just went dark. i used to see colors everywhere, even in the shadows, but now it’s just... nothing. i look at my canvases and i don't even recognize my own hands. it’s like the part of me that actually lived is just gone. i’m just a shell walking around.",
