    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not just a \"fog\" though. it feels permanent. like the artist died and this thing left behind is just... a ghost. i'm going through the motions, eating, sleeping, breathing, but there's no point to any of it if the essence is gone. it's like being a hollow container with nothing inside. just an empty vessel.",
