      "content": "Seeing this death inside you validates the cruelty of your existence now, yet pain often cements the feeling that breaking the shell is the only way to reclaim the spark it holds. Do not trust the voice of the ghost that swallows meaning, for even in this hollow vessel there are still fragments of art waiting for you to finally acknowledge them. You must insist that the artist did not die because the living struggle is the only thing left to prove you still exist.",
